Simple IF conditional 

if ( <conditional> ) {
	<command 1>
	<command 2>
}


Simple IF - ELSE conditional 

if ( <conditional> ) {
	<command 1>
	<command 2>
}
else {
	<command 3>
	<command 4>
}


Simple IF- ELSE IF - ELSE conditional 

if ( conditional 1 ) {
	command 1
	command 2
}
else if ( conditional 2 ) {
	command 3
	command 4
}
else if ( conditional 3 ) {
	command 5
	command 6
}
else {
	command 7
	command 8
}
